# Security Validation Notes

## Objective
Confirm that segmentation and monitoring controls function correctly.

## Validation Checks

VLAN Isolation
- Guest VLAN could not access Admin VLAN
- Staff VLAN blocked from Admin network

Firewall Enforcement
- pfSense logs confirmed blocked traffic attempts

SIEM Monitoring
- Endpoint successfully transmitted logs to Wazuh server
- Dashboard displayed real-time data

## Analyst Conclusion
Network segmentation and monitoring controls function as designed. Access restrictions, logging visibility, and system health checks confirm a properly secured internal architecture.
